headline: Will Wynn (WYNN) and Marjan’s New Joint Venture Deepen Their Competitive Edge in Global Luxury Hospitality?
summary: Wynn Resorts and Marjan LLC recently announced their second joint venture on Al Marjan Island, the Janu Al Marjan Island resort, operated by Aman Group and scheduled to open in late 2028, expanding the hospitality footprint alongside the soon-to-launch Wynn Al Marjan Island. This partnership marks another step in establishing Ras Al Khaimah as a premier lifestyle destination, furthering Wynn Resorts' strategy to deliver luxury experiences through international collaborations and residential...
